node.title: Police appeal for information after non-verbal boy goes missing in Upper Hutt
node.description: Leonidas went missing just after 6:30pm on Tuesday.
node.content: ["Wellington police are appealing to the public for information locating young Upper Hutt boy Leonidas.", "In a post to Facebook, Wellington police said the young boy was last seen in Ng\u0101ti Tama Park in Lower Hutt just after 6:30pm on Tuesday.", "\"He is wearing a black shirt and grey shorts.\"", "Police say Leonidas is non-verbal and won't respond to people speaking.", "Video from the scene shows Fire and Emergency and police at the scene as well as what looks like local residents combing through surrounding bush.", "Police urge anyone who sees Leonidas to call 111."]
